*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& 包含               ZJQR0000_FRM
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form frm_add_num
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> A
*&      --> B
*&      <-- C
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM frm_add_num  USING    p_a
                           p_b
                  CHANGING p_c.

  p_c = p_a + p_b.

ENDFORM.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form frm_write_hello
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM frm_write_hello .
  WRITE:/ 'hello, abap'.
ENDFORM.